{"id":129559,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Steve_Carell","text":"Steven John \"Steve\" Carell (born August 16, 1962) is an American actor, comedian, producer, writer and director. His father is of Italian and German descent, and his mother was of Polish ancestry. Carell is best known for his comedic work as Michael Scott in \"The Office\" and \"The Daily Show\".\nHe played Andy Stitzer in \"The 40-Year-Old Virgin\", Gru in \"Despicable Me\" and \"Despicable Me 2\" and John Eleuth\u00E8re du Pont in \"Foxcatcher\". He has appeared on \"Saturday Night Live\".\nHe starred as Donald Rumsfeld in the 2018 comedy \"Vice\". In 2020, he starred as General Mark R. Naird in the Netflix sitcom \"Space Force\".","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Americans","surface_form":"American","offset":56},{"uri":"Actor","surface_form":"actor","offset":65},{"uri":"Comedian","surface_form":"comedian","offset":72},{"uri":"Television_producer","surface_form":"producer","offset":82},{"uri":"Writer","surface_form":"writer","offset":92},{"uri":"Television_director","surface_form":"director","offset":103},{"uri":"Michael_Scott_(The_Office)","surface_form":"Michael Scott","offset":242},{"uri":"The_Office_(U.S._TV_series)","surface_form":"The Office","offset":260},{"uri":"The_Daily_Show","surface_form":"The Daily Show","offset":277},{"uri":"The_40-Year-Old_Virgin","surface_form":"The 40-Year-Old Virgin","offset":321},{"uri":"Despicable_Me","surface_form":"Despicable Me","offset":354},{"uri":"Despicable_Me_2","surface_form":"Despicable Me 2","offset":374},{"uri":"John_Eleuth%C3%A8re_du_Pont","surface_form":"John Eleuth\u00E8re du Pont","offset":395},{"uri":"Foxcatcher","surface_form":"Foxcatcher","offset":422},{"uri":"Saturday_Night_Live","surface_form":"Saturday Night Live","offset":455},{"uri":"Donald_Rumsfeld","surface_form":"Donald Rumsfeld","offset":491},{"uri":"Vice_(movie)","surface_form":"Vice","offset":527},{"uri":"Netflix","surface_form":"Netflix","offset":586}